## Sales Analysis Dashboard

This Power BI report provides a comprehensive view of sales performance through four interactive report pages: **Sales Analysis**, **Product Details**, **TreeMap**, and **Sales Trend**.

The dashboard tracks key business metrics including **Total Sales, Profit, Profit Margin, Product Count, and Salesperson Performance**. Users can filter results by **Region** and **Year** to analyze performance across different markets and time periods.

The report explores sales data from multiple perspectives, including product-wise sales distribution, category-level performance, profitability analysis, and subcategory contributions through treemap visualizations. A detailed product view enables users to examine product sales, quantities, profit, and margins at a granular level.

Additionally, the Sales Trend page highlights sales patterns over time and compares regional performance, helping identify growth opportunities and business trends. Overall, this dashboard is designed to support data-driven decision-making by providing actionable insights into product performance, profitability, regional sales, and historical sales trends.
